Features
  • Selectable color temperatures (3000K, 3500K, 4000K, and 5000K)
  • Selectable lumen outputs (2,000Lm or 3,000Lm)

ATTRIBUTES

The NICOR CLR8-Select is a complete 8-inch recessed LED downlight system built to commercial grade specifications. The canless design allows for direct installation into drywall, ceiling grids, or existing mounting frames, bypassing the need for a recessed housing. Installation requires a simple circular cut-out in the ceiling using the included template. This high-output CLR8-Select features a switch on the back to select between 3000K, 3500K, 4000K, and 5000K color temperatures. Another switch lets you toggle between 2,000 and 3,000 lumens, allowing you to control the power and brightness. The CLR8-Select is also wet-location rated, energy star rated, and airtight. It features full-range dimming (0-10VDC) and a built-in multi-volt driver (120-347-Volts). In short, it’s the most versatile and complete commercial downlight system to date. It can be installed anywhere, in any setting. Use it for new construction, remodel, or retrofit applications. Available in Black, Nickel, Aged Copper, and White. The CLR8-Select is protected by NICOR’s 5-year limited warranty.
